    "product_size_description_MCM8aH": {
      "type": "product-size-description",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_item_zXVp6z": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why you'll love it!",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>Shapermint Essentials Everyday Comfort Straps Wireless Shaping Bra</strong> is your new favorite everyday wireless bra, with adjustable, convertible straps for even more comfort and support. Adjust your straps for a customized fit and additional lift, and style the straps as a racerback to disappear under tricky tops.</p><p>Its second-skin soft nylon-elastane fabric is just as breathable as it is supportive. The wireless bra with support and structured cups gives you a seamless, smooth, and ultra-comfortable look every day.!</p><ul><li>Adjustable straps for customized support and comfort.</li><li>Convertible straps can be worn as racerback.</li><li>Structured cups offer control and lift.</li><li>Enjoy easy on and off with a hook & eye back closure.</li><li>Seamless means no itch or unsightly lines.</li><li>Foam cups for all-day comfort & confidence.</li><li>Designed to fit sizes S to 4XL (plus size), this everyday wireless bra comes with our Good Fit Guarantee.</li></ul>",
            "open_default": true
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_zVMi7c": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Hassle-Free Exchanges & Returns Policy",
            "content": "<p>We know that even with guidance, finding the perfect fit can take a try or two. That’s why we offer easy exchanges within 60 days, so you can shop with confidence.Swap for a different size, color, or style you love within 60 days of delivery for free, or return your item for a $6 USD processing fee. Just make sure it’s in good condition, with original tags, packaging, and hygiene seals fully intact. We’ll take care of the rest!<br/><br/>See full Exchanges & Returns policy<a href=\"https://help.shapermint.com/hc/en-us/articles/900002245546-What-is-Shapermint-s-EXCHANGES-and-returns-policy\">here</a>. Have questions?<a href=\"https://help.shapermint.com/hc/en-us/requests/new\">Contact us</a>.</p>",
            "open_default": false
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_WtJDN3": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Details",
            "content": "<p><strong>Composition </strong><br/>- 95% Polyamide, <br/>- 5% Elastane</p><p><strong>Style Number</strong><br/>10024</p>",
            "open_default": false
          }
        }
      },
